            . I am a constable. The prisoner was brought to me and confessed his guilt.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had just passed the shop, when a man asked me to carry the box to the end of the street, and he would give me a few halfpence; I took it without hesitation, when the prosecutor seized me, the man ran away. I did not state this to the Magistrate as I was advised not.</p>
